199/200 [============================>.] - ETA: 5s - loss: 0.0329   
200/200 [==============================] - 1231s - loss: 0.0330 - val_loss: 0.0326
Epoch 6/20
199/200 [============================>.] - ETA: 5s - loss: 0.0307   
200/200 [==============================] - 1258s - loss: 0.0307 - val_loss: 0.0430

199/200 [============================>.] - ETA: 5s - loss: 0.0325   
200/200 [==============================] - 1223s - loss: 0.0325 - val_loss: 0.0363

199/200 [============================>.] - ETA: 5s - loss: 0.0298   
200/200 [==============================] - 1225s - loss: 0.0298 - val_loss: 0.0447

199/200 [============================>.] - ETA: 5s - loss: 0.0277   
200/200 [==============================] - 1227s - loss: 0.0277 - val_loss: 0.0351
